### Archimedes Backend API Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/healthcheck/

###

### 2. Register a New School
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolCode": "240901042",
  "name": "LAMAR MIDDLE",
  "address": "1818 N ARKANSAS AVE, LAREDO, TX, 78043-3097",
  "principal": "MR EDUARDO LOPEZ",
  "email": "elopez2@Laredoisd.org",
  "phoneNumber": "(956) 273-6200"
}

###

### 3. Register a New User (Student) STU001
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oscar.fimbres",
  "email": "oscar.fimbres@gmail.com",
  "password": "TempPassword123!",
  "givenName": "Oscar",
  "familyName": "Fimbres",
  "schoolId": "1",
  "userType": "students"
}

###

### 4. Register a New User (Teacher)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "guadalupe.trevino",
  "email": "guadalupe.trevino@gmail.com",
  "password": "TempPassword123!",
  "givenName": "Guadalupe",
  "familyName": "Trevino",
  "schoolId": "1",
  "userType": "teachers"
}

###

### 5. Send Verification Code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/sendCode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oscar.fimbres"
}

###

### 5. Verify User Account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/verifyCode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oscar.fimbres",
  "confirmationCode": "177760"
}

###

### 6. User Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oscar.fimbres",
  "password": "TempPassword123!"
}

###

### 7. Get User Attributes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/oscar.fimbres/attributes

###

### 8. Get Student Information
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools/1/students/S001

###

### 9. Enroll Student in Period (Simplified API)
### Student S001 in period P001 for school 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools/1/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S001",
  "periodId": "P001"
}

###

### 11. Get Teacher Information (Simplified)  
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools/1/teachers/T003

###

### 12. Get Students in a Period (Simplified)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools/1/students/periods/P001

###

### 13. Unenroll Student from Period (Simplified)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools/SCH001/enrollments/S001/P001

###

### 13. Get All Topics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/topic/

###

### 14. Get Exercises for Topic
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/topic/ALGEBRAIC_EXPRESSIONS/exercises

###

### 15. Get Exercises for Topic + Subtopic
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/topic/ALGEBRAIC_EXPRESSIONS/subtopic/AX1/exercises

###

### 16. Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/forgotPassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "diego.hinojosa"
}

###

### 17. Confirm Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/confirmForgotPassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "diego.hinojosa",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "confirmationCode": "123456"
}

###

### 18. Create a New School
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/school
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolCode": "LAMAR_MIDDLE",
  "name": "LAMAR MIDDLE",
  "address": "1818 N ARKANSAS AVE, LAREDO, TX, 78043-3097",
  "principalName": "MR EDUARDO LOPEZ",
  "contactEmail": "elopez2@Laredoisd.org",
  "phoneNumber": "(956) 273-6200"
}

###

### 19. Get School Information
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/school/SCH001

###

### 20. Create a New Teacher
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolId": "SCH001",
  "firstName": "Guadalupe",
  "lastName": "Trevino",
  "email": "guadalupe.trevino@gmail.com",
  "username": "guadalupe.trevino",
  "maxPeriods": 6
}

###

### 21. Create a New Student
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolId": "SCH001",
  "firstName": "Diego",
  "lastName": "Hinojosa",
  "email": "diego.hinojosa@gmail.com",
  "username": "diego.hinojosa"
}

###

### Authentication Examples with Token (if using JWT)
### After login, you'll get a token. Use it like this:

### 22. Authenticated Request Example
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/STU001
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

###

### 23. Test Authenticated Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test/hello
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

###

### ===== JPA ENDPOINTS =====

### 24. Get All Schools (JPA)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools

###

### 25. Get School by Code (JPA)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/schools/by-code/240901042

###

### 26. Create Student (JPA)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Garcia",
  "email": "maria.garcia@example.com",
  "username": "maria.garcia",
  "schoolCode": "240901042",
  "gradeLevel": 5
}

###

### 27. Create Teacher (JPA)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teachers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Wilson",
  "email": "john.wilson@example.com",
  "username": "john.wilson",
  "schoolCode": "240901042",
  "department": "Mathematics"
}

###

### 28. Get Students by School (JPA)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/by-school/240901042

###

### 29. Get Teachers by School (JPA)  
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teachers/by-school/240901042

###
